## Config Changes

### tsconfig.json
```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "strict": true,
    "baseUrl": "src",
    "jsx": "react-jsx",
    "types": ["vitest/globals"]
  }
}
```

### package.json scripts
```json
{
  "test": "vitest run",
  "test:watch": "vitest",
  "test-ci": "vitest run --coverage",
  "eslint": "eslint src/",
  "eslint-fix": "eslint src/ --fix"
}
```

### vite.config.js test block
```js
test: {
  globals: true,
  environment: 'jsdom',
  setupFiles: './src/setupTests.ts',
  include: ['src/**/*.test.{ts,tsx}']
}
```
